										<MultiDataTrigger>
											<MultiDataTrigger.Conditions>
												<Condition Binding="{Binding IsSelectionAllowed}" Value="False"/>
												<Condition Binding="{Binding IsExpanded}" Value="True"/>
											</MultiDataTrigger.Conditions>
											<MultiDataTrigger.Setters>
